00:13:54,794 --> 00:13:58,170
Like what the youth
today would call a “sigma.”

272
00:13:58,195 --> 00:13:59,296
A sigma artist.

273
00:13:59,296 --> 00:14:02,971
Sigma means you’re very independent,

274
00:14:03,018 --> 00:14:05,678
