00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,681
[Director] Action!

281
00:14:46,434 --> 00:14:49,708
Luna—she’s independent.

282
00:14:50,973 --> 00:14:52,850
She’s responsible.

283
00:14:52,933 --> 00:14:54,254
She knows her worth.

284
00:14:54,295 --> 00:14:55,772
But even with all that,

285
00:14:55,797 --> 00:14:58,355
