he takes care of and helps grow,

297
00:15:47,154 --> 00:15:47,947
his flowers.

298
00:15:47,947 --> 00:15:50,532
So his love language
is giving flowers

299
00:15:50,557 --> 00:15:52,059
to the people he cares about,

300
00:15:52,084 --> 00:15:54,003
during the key moments of his life.

301
00:15:54,326 --> 00:15:56,221
I just want to make you
feel that you’re special.

302
00:15:56,246 --> 00:15:59,257
By giving you flowers
that I grow myself.

303
00:16:00,276 --> 00:16:04,772
Main thing about Raffy is he doesn’t want
to be a burden to anyone.

304
00:16:04,797 --> 00:16:07,210
