00:18:45,851 --> 00:18:47,486
So it’s really for everyone,

347
00:18:47,511 --> 00:18:50,003
no matter your age,

348
00:18:50,028 --> 00:18:51,851
as long as you’ve experienced love before.

349
00:18:51,964 --> 00:18:54,925
You’ll definitely see the
different stages of love in this.

350
00:18:55,115 --> 00:18:59,388
It’s the kind of love where
you give your 100 percent,

351
00:18:59,413 --> 00:19:03,750
but still make sure you leave
something for yourself.

