00:19:08,522 --> 00:19:11,834
especially coming
from Raffy’s end.

354
00:19:11,859 --> 00:19:12,859
You know.

355
00:19:18,407 --> 00:19:19,908
As you see, as the story progresses,

356
00:19:19,933 --> 00:19:21,601
you see how much he cares for Luna.

357
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:32,021
And even as time goes by,

358
00:19:32,107 --> 00:19:35,491
the love they had for each other,
