361
00:19:59,965 --> 00:20:01,607
The general tone of the film—

362
00:20:01,867 --> 00:20:07,039
since Ashtine and Andres came from
Ang Mutya ng Section E,

363
00:20:07,064 --> 00:20:11,210
which is a Wattpad adaptation
and kind of larger-than-life,

364
00:20:11,235 --> 00:20:15,198
like a fantasy for
high schoolers—

365
00:20:15,297 --> 00:20:18,586
this time in Minamahal:
100 Bulaklak para kay Luna,

366
00:20:18,675 --> 00:20:22,403
our approach is more
realistic, more mature.

367
00:20:22,476 --> 00:20:25,140
When I pitched the project to Viva,

368
00:20:25,165 --> 00:20:30,732
I said it’s a high school romance
from the point of view of a mature person.

369
00:20:30,757 --> 00:20:32,481
That’s why our cinematography,

370
00:20:32,506 --> 00:20:33,665
our color grading—

371
00:20:33,690 --> 00:20:35,880
it reflects that mature point of view.

372
00:20:35,905 --> 00:20:39,400
It’s not overly
vibrant—it’s very nostalgic.

373
00:20:39,425 --> 00:20:43,721
The tones are subtle so
the audience can really

374
00:20:43,746 --> 00:20:46,875
feel the realism of
what’s happening.

375
00:20:47,275 --> 00:20:48,833
Are you getting paid for this?

376
00:20:49,831 --> 00:20:52,918
And does this count as an
extra-curricular activity?

377
00:20:55,121 --> 00:20:57,996
I’m really into plants.
Especially flowers.

378
00:21:02,761 --> 00:21:03,761
Here.

379
00:21:04,470 --> 00:21:05,470
Flowers.

380
00:21:05,537 --> 00:21:06,538
It’s for you.

