00:25:06,963 --> 00:25:11,660
He’s so good. And I’m really
glad that it’s already here.

458
00:25:11,685 --> 00:25:14,575
Direk JPL thank you so much! I love you!

459
00:25:57,745 --> 00:26:01,639
I would say that Minamahal:
100 Bulaklak para kay Luna

